    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i've been looking at the environmental side of things too. it seems like a pretty clear-cut way to lower emissions and hit climate goals, so why do people actually fight it so hard? like, besides the money thing, is there anything else that makes it a bad idea?",
